{"parentUuid":"dac2a0f0-8285-4bbd-82d7-cd712cf1e63c","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough","sessionId":"18eb6a87-cd5a-46cc-bd17-a684e5ddc651","version":"2.1.73","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"af296d5808011d21f","slug":"immutable-imagining-crayon","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01UzXAYJb4Pcy9YVdroPCYLS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've read all the GraphQL schema files. Here's the comprehensive summary:\n\n## GraphQL Schema Summary\n\n### Scalars\n- `DateTime` - for timestamp fields\n- `JSON` - for flexible metadata objects\n\n### Enums\n\n**ItemType**\n- BOOKMARK, VOICE_NOTE, TEXT_NOTE, DRIVE_DOC, HIGHLIGHT, FILE\n\n**ItemStatus**\n- PENDING, PROCESSING, READY, ERROR\n\n**SensitivityLevel**\n- PUBLIC, NORMAL, SENSITIVE, PRIVATE\n\n**ItemSortField**\n- CREATED_AT, UPDATED_AT, CAPTURED_AT, TITLE\n\n**SortDirection**\n- ASC, DESC\n\n---\n\n### Item CRUD Operations\n\n#### Queries\n\n| Query | Purpose | Parameters |\n|---|---|---|\n| `item(id: ID!)` | Fetch single item by ID | Required: id |\n| `items(...)` | List items with filters and pagination | Optional: filter, limit, offset, sort |\n| `search(...)` | Full-text or semantic search | Required: query; Optional: filter, limit, threshold |\n\n#### Mutations\n\n| Mutation | Purpose | Input |\n|---|---|---|\n| `captureBookmark(input)` | Create bookmark item | BookmarkInput |\n| `captureNote(input)` | Create text note | NoteInput |\n| `captureVoiceNote(input)` | Create voice note | VoiceNoteInput |\n| `updateItem(id, input)` | Update item metadata | id, UpdateItemInput |\n| `deleteItem(id)` | Delete item | id |\n| `updateSensitivity(id, sensitivity)` | Change sensitivity level | id, SensitivityLevel |\n| `tagItem(id, tags)` | Add/update tags | id, [String!] |\n\n---\n\n### Input Types for Item Operations\n\n**ItemFilter** - Used in `items()` and `search()` queries\n- `types: [ItemType!]` - Filter by item type\n- `tags: [String!]` - Filter by tags\n- `sensitivity: [SensitivityLevel!]` - Filter by sensitivity\n- `source: String` - Filter by source\n- `dateFrom: DateTime` - Filter from date\n- `dateTo: DateTime` - Filter to date\n- `status: [ItemStatus!]` - Filter by status\n\n**ItemSort** - Used in `items()` query\n- `field: ItemSortField!` - Sort field\n- `direction: SortDirection!` - ASC or DESC\n\n**BookmarkInput** - For `captureBookmark()` mutation\n- `url: String!` - Required\n- `title: String` - Optional\n- `selection: String` - Selected text from page\n- `referrer: String` - Source page\n- `tags: [String!]` - Optional tags\n- `sensitivity: SensitivityLevel` - Optional (defaults to NORMAL)\n\n**NoteInput** - For `captureNote()` mutation\n- `title: String` - Optional\n- `content: String!` - Required\n- `tags: [String!]` - Optional\n- `sensitivity: SensitivityLevel` - Optional\n\n**VoiceNoteInput** - For `captureVoiceNote()` mutation\n- `audioKey: String!` - Required (S3 key)\n- `title: String` - Optional\n- `tags: [String!]` - Optional\n- `sensitivity: SensitivityLevel` - Optional\n- `source: String` - Optional\n\n**UpdateItemInput** - For `updateItem()` mutation\n- `title: String` - Optional\n- `tags: [String!]` - Optional\n- `sensitivity: SensitivityLevel` - Optional\n\n---\n\n### Item Type & Response\n\n**Item** - Returned by all queries and mutations\n```\nid, type, status, sensitivity, title, contentText, contentUrl, tags[],\nmetadata (JSON), autoMetadata (JSON), source, sourceUrl, createdAt,\nupdatedAt, capturedAt\n```\n\n**SearchResult** - Returned by list and search queries\n- `items: [Item!]!` - List of items\n- `total: Int!` - Total matching items\n- `hasMore: Boolean!` - Whether more results available\n\n---\n\n### Authentication Operations\n\n**Queries**\n- `me: User` - Get current authenticated user\n\n**Mutations**\n- `register(input: RegisterInput!): AuthPayload!`\n- `login(input: LoginInput!): AuthPayload!`\n\n**Input Types**\n- **RegisterInput**: email, password, displayName (optional)\n- **LoginInput**: email, password\n\n**Response Types**\n- **User**: id, email, displayName, createdAt, updatedAt\n- **AuthPayload**: token (JWT), user (User object)\n\n---\n\n### MCP Client Operations\n\n**Queries**\n- `mcpClients: [MCPClient!]!` - List all MCP clients\n\n**Mutations**\n- `createMCPClient(input: CreateMCPClientInput!): MCPClientWithKey!`\n- `deactivateMCPClient(id: ID!): Boolean!`\n\n**Types**\n- **MCPClient**: id, name, tools[], maxSensitivity, active, lastUsedAt, createdAt\n- **MCPClientWithKey**: client (MCPClient), apiKey (String)\n- **CreateMCPClientInput**: name, tools[] (optional), maxSensitivity (optional)\n\n---\n\n### File Locations\n- `/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough/api/graph/schema/schema.graphql` - Root queries and mutations\n- `/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough/api/graph/schema/item.graphql` - Item types and inputs\n- `/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough/api/graph/schema/auth.graphql` - Auth types\n- `/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough/api/graph/schema/mcp_client.graphql` - MCP types\n- `/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough/api/graph/schema/enums.graphql` - All enums\n- `/home/ketan/project/flotsam/.claude/worktrees/worktree/demo-walkthrough/api/graph/schema/scalars.graphql` - Custom scalars"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7727,"cache_read_input_tokens":37623,"output_tokens":1569,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":7727},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYx8YmCn4pW4CkwGwZeQA","type":"assistant","uuid":"2e0ea4dc-b944-43fc-b96d-